   <b>(3) Paragraph:</b> Time_offset
 </p>
 <p>
   <b>(5) Comment:</b>
 </p>
 <p>
ENTITY Time_offset;
hour_offset : INTEGER;
minute_offset : OPTIONAL INTEGER;
sense : offset_orientation;
DERIVE
actual_minute_offset: INTEGER := NVL(minute_offset,0);
WHERE
WR1: { 0 &lt;= hour_offset &lt; 24 };
WR2: { 0 &lt;= minute_offset &lt;= 59 };
WR3: NOT (((hour_offset &lt;&gt; 0) OR (actual_minute_offset &lt;&gt;0))
AND (sense = exact));
END_ENTITY;
WR2 should relate to actual_minute_offset. Minute_offset may not be set!</p>
